edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等睇拒絕入港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那唔敢咁做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChing岩岩放監？對上一次拒絕入港吾系好耐炸喎😅</blockquote><br />\n支那想近距離偵測新野，點會唔放入香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6300e35cce2727e6a998f34db571c9d90eb602c8","tid":419888,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等睇拒絕入港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那唔敢咁做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChing岩岩放監？對上一次拒絕入港吾系好耐炸喎😅</blockquote><br />\n拒絕入港，然後經台灣海峽返日本<br />\n嚇到支共賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923b6cc7f426db048e4fd6976b7c4febd0038d98","tid":419888,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:24:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa9c81531a2685f180ef597e9761003e2c934faf","tid":419888,"uid":18761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"北韓導彈會射來香港 先發制人嗎？ 巧驚驚"},{"pid":"b4477dcc0f07d3d0d72418b63a778f0489220256","tid":419888,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/095229_45fc01d4e9d9d9bde0ba7cbeccdb0c1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F095229_45fc01d4e9d9d9bde0ba7cbeccdb0c1f.jpg&h=9994671f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/095230_dcdb0c379bceb0390541ab0e02d93367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i